# Visualizing quadratic surfaces

## 开发环境

**处理器**：Interl(R) Core(TM) i5-6200U CPU @ 2.30GHz, RAM 4.00GB.

**开发环境**：
- Micorsoft Visual Studio 2015;
- Qt Creator 4.2.1 (MSVC 2015 (64-bit));

